I added a yellow grosgrain ribbon trim and bow (but I have many other colors of trim available just ask) Best of all it has two outside gathered pockets perfect for a cell phone, baby bottle etc. Choose your closure: Zipper, magnetic snap, Velcro, button and loop, ribbon or a cloth tie. The bag is fully lined and there are 6 interior pockets with embroidered tops, which are perfect for bottles, sunglasses, cellphones, wallets, etc. It has a heavy fleece between the fabrics to make it sturdy and it stands on it's own even when empty. This is a perfect bag for anyone who loves room for everything!
